# Reusable Project Concepts

- [Repository Purpose](repository-purpose.md) records why a project, repository, service, or major component exists.
- [Repository Decision](repository-decision.md) records settled choices that constrain future work.
- [Repository Directive](repository-directive.md) records implementation handoffs that are ready to be picked up later.
- [Repository Delta](repository-delta.md) records what actually changed after implementation.
